summary: Eradahl will give you a mission to find his lost sword and return it to him for a good amount of coins. (Voice acted quest)
descriptionHtml:
Eradahl is a wood elf who lives in the inn of Falkreath. He will give you a mission to find his lost sword and return it to him for a good amount of coins. This quest also contains a new house in the forrests of Falkreath, which you can move into after completion of the quest. (Voice acted quest)

Good luck!
author: Zxeddery
